snippet.title: Lemnis Gate | Pre-Order & Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Lemnis Gate is the revolutionary turn-based combat strategy FPS taking place in a time loop. Harness the abilities of powerful operatives and compete in mind-bending 4D battles as you disrupt the past to change the future. 

Pre-order here: https://lemnisgategame.com/pre-order 

Coming to PC, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on August 3. Pre-Order Now.

Learn more here: https://www.lemnisgategame.com/​​

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/950180/Lemnis_Gate/
